dct_title_s: Normandy D Day, June 6, 1944 = Normandie Jour J, 6 Juin 1944 / réalisée et éditée par l'Institut géographique national
dct_description_sm: Map shows the organization and movements of the Allied Expeditionary Force. Legends and chronology in French, English, and German. Panel title. Includes text, chronology, inset of "Opération Neptune," organizational diagram of the Allied Forces, color illustrations, and coats of arms.
